a.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118101838.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20issued%20an%20executive%20order%20renaming%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20to%20the%20'Gulf%20of%20America'%20and%20declared%20February%209%20as%20'Gulf%20of%20America%20Day.'%20The%20change%20highlights%20the%20region's%20historical%20importance%20to%20the%20United%20States%20and%20directs%20the%20official%20transition%20to%20occur%20within%2030%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frestoring-names-donald-trump-renames-gulf-of-mexico-declares-february-9-as-gulf-of-america-day%2Farticleshow%2F118101838.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frestoring-names-donald-trump-renames-gulf-of-mexico-declares-february-9-as-gulf-of-america-day%2Famp_articleshow%2F118101838.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frestoring-names-donald-trump-renames-gulf-of-mexico-declares-february-9-as-gulf-of-america-day%2Famp_articleshow%2F118101838.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Broke...%26quot%3B%3A%20Rohit's%20Honest%20Take%20On%20Century%20Against%20England%20In%202nd%20ODI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Benjoyed%26quot%3B%20scoring%20a%20hundred%20for%20the%20team%2C%20and%20attributed%20his%20century%20to%20him%20%26quot%3Bbreaking%20down%26quot%3B%20his%20batting%20approach%20in%20Cuttak%20on%20Sunday.%20Came%20into%20the%20second%20ODI%20against%20England%20with%20a%20string%20low-scores%20against%20his%20name%2C%20Rohit%20shushed%20his%20doubters%20with%20a%20masterly%2090-ball%2032nd%20ODI%20hundred%2C%20also%20containing%2012%20fours%20and%20seven%20sixes.%20It%20helped%20India%20register%20a%20nine-wicket%20win%2C%20and%20grab%20the%20three-match%20series%202-0.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20good%20and%20really%20enjoyed%20being%20out%20there%2C%20scoring%20some%20runs%20for%20the%20team.%20It%20was%20an%20important%20game%20with%20the%20series%20on%20the%20line%20but%20I%20broke%20it%20down%20to%20pieces%20about%20how%20I%20wanted%20to%20bat%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%20during%20the%20presentation%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(ODIs%20are)%20longer%20than%20T20s%20and%20shorter%20than%20Tests%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20break%20it%20down.%20I%20wanted%20to%20bat%20as%20deep%20as%20possible%20and%20that%20was%20my%20focus.%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20place%20the%20ball%20precisely%20in%20the%20gaps%20as%20the%20England%20bowlers%20were%20aiming%20at%20his%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20the%20pitch%20-%20when%20you%20play%20on%20black%20soil%2C%20it%20tends%20to%20skid%20on%20a%20bit%20and%20you%20have%20to%20show%20the%20full%20face%20of%20the%20bat%20initially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20bowled%20into%20the%20body%20and%20kept%20it%20on%20the%20stumps%20and%20that's%20where%20I%20prepared%20my%20plan%20and%20tried%20to%20access%20the%20gaps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbaikar%20praised%20his%20opening%20partner%20Shubman%20Gill%20for%20assisting%20him%20to%20get%20the%20team%20off%20to%20a%20flier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20very%20good%20support%20from%20Gill%20and%20Shreyas%20(Iyer)%20as%20well.%20I%20enjoy%20batting%20with%20Gill.%20He%20is%20a%20very%20classy%20player%20and%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20get%20overawed%20by%20the%20situation%20and%20the%20numbers%20are%20there%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20said%20the%20bowlers%20applied%20the%20break%20to%20a%20nicety%20over%20England%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%20after%20the%20visitors%20got%20off%20the%20block%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20middle%20overs%20are%20quite%20important%20and%20that's%20where%20the%20game%20can%20go%20either%20side.%20If%20you%20squeeze%20the%20middle%20overs%2C%20you%20need%20not%20worry%20much%20about%20the%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20middle%20overs%20is%20very%20crucial%20and%20even%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20we%20squeezed%20them%20and%20got%20wickets.%20When%20you%20keep%20taking%20wickets%2C%20the%20run-scoring%20is%20not%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20giving%20away%20the%20specifics%2C%20Rohit%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20see%20overall%20improvements%20in%20the%20team%20ahead%20of%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20beginning%20on%20February%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20specific%20we%20want%20to%20work%20on%20but%20overall%20we%20want%20to%20keep%20getting%20better%20as%20a%20player%20and%20team.%20As%20long%20as%20guys%20are%20clear%20about%20what%20they%20are%20supposed%20to%20do%2C%20if%20they%20keep%20doing%20that%20not%20much%20to%20think%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit%2C%20who%20understandably%20was%20player%20of%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERohit%20made%20it%20look%20easy%3A%20Gill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVice-captain%20Shubman%20Gill%20lauded%20skipper%20Rohit%20for%20cracking%20a%20hundred%20full%20of%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWas%20feeling%20good%20when%20I%20was%20batting%20and%2C%20obviously%2C%20batting%20with%20Rohit%20bhai%2C%20he%20makes%20it%20look%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20he%20took%20on%20the%20bowlers%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20that%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20how%20he%20has%20batted%20in%20ODIs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGill%2C%20who%20made%20a%20fluent%2060%20and%20added%20136%20runs%20in%20just%2016.4%20overs%2C%20said%20it%20was%20good%20pitch%20to%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20good%20wicket%20to%20bat%20on%2C%20the%20odd%20ball%20was%20keeping%20a%20bit%20low%20but%20overall%20a%20good%20wicket.%20The%20chat%20was%20simple%2