ral%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation.%20They%20fabricated%20false%20documents%20and%20seals%2C%20using%20the%20name%20of%20AR%20Dairy%20to%20manipulate%20the%20tender%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployees%20of%20Vaishnavi%20Dairy%20also%20created%20fake%20records%20claiming%20they%20have%20sourced%20ghee%20from%20Bhole%20Baba%20Dairy%20in%20Roorkee.%20The%20investigators%20found%20that%20Bhole%20Baba%20Dairy%20did%20not%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20supply%20such%20quantities%20of%20ghee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20identified%20the%20irregularities%20and%20arrested%20four%20individuals%20from%20three%20dairies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllegations%20that%20ghee%20adulterated%20with%20animal%20fat%20are%20being%20use%20to%20make%20the%20laddoos%20for%20prasadam%20at%20the%20Tirupati%20exploded%20across%20headlines%20last%20year%2C%20sparking%20a%20massive%20row%20that%20speedily%20became%20political.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Andhra%20government%20had%20red-flagged%20a%20report%20from%20a%20lab%20in%20Gujarat%20that%20said%20samples%20of%20the%20the%20ghee%20bought%20from%20a%20supplier%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Dindigul%20contained%20traces%20of%20fish%20oil%2C%20beef%20tallow%2C%20and%20lard.%20The%20lab%20also%20added%20a%20disclaimer%20about%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20positives%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20slammed%20the%20mix%20of%20religion%20and%20politics%20and%20ordered%20a%20special%20team%20be%20formed%20to%20investigate%20the%20animal%20fat%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20special%20team%20comprised%20two%20CBI%20officers%2C%20two%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Police%20personnel%2C%20and%20a%20senior%20official%20from%20the%20centre-run%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20kitchen%20at%20Tirupati%20makes%20around%20three%20lakh%20laddoos%20daily%2C%20with%20around%201%2C500%20kg%20of%20ghee%20and%20vast%20amounts%20of%20cashew%20nuts%2C%20raisins%2C%20cardamoms%2C%20gram%20flour%2C%20and%20s