%2Famp_articleshow%2F118094673.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwho-is-daniel-noboa-conservative-millionaire-president-seeking-reelection-in-ecuador%2Famp_articleshow%2F118094673.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biren%20Singh%20Quits%20As%20Chief%20Minister%202%20Years%20After%20Manipur%20Violence%20Began%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EManipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20resigned%20today%20-%20two%20years%20after%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20state%20--%20to%20quell%20dissidence%20in%20the%20state%20BJP%20against%20his%20leadership%20as%20his%20government%20faces%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20Congress%20no-confidence%20motion%20and%20floor%20test.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20handed%20his%20resignation%20to%20the%20Governor%20this%20evening.%20The%20Congress%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bbelated%26quot%3B%20resignation%20was%20a%20vindication%20of%20its%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20resignation%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20the%20budget%20session%20of%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20that%20was%20to%20begin%20from%20today%2C%20has%20been%20cancelled%2C%20Governor%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Bhalla%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20has%20the%20numbers%20despite%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20support%20by%20Conrad%20Sangma's%20National%20Peoples'%20Party%2C%20there%20was%20a%20possibility%20that%20the%20MLAs%20who%20sought%20a%20change%20in%20leadership%2C%20would%20have%20disregarded%20a%20party%20whip%20in%20case%20of%20a%20floor%20test.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20avert%20that%20possibility%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20stepped%20down%20after%20conferring%20with%20the%20central%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20had%20gone%20to%20Delhi%20this%20morning%20where%20he%20met%20party%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20and%20its%20chief%20strategist%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20May%202023%2C%20around%2012%20MLAs%20have%20been%20strongly%20pushing%20for%20a%20change%20in%20leadership%2C%20and%20there%20are%20around%20six%20fence%20sitters%2C%20party%20sources%20said.%20The%20sources%20also%20added%20that%20the%20Speaker%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20have%20had%20%26quot%3Bdifferences%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20rebels%20have%20even%20met%20Amit%20Shah%20with%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Congress%20threat%20of%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20in%20the%20assembly%20session%2C%20sources%20said%20there%20was%20a%20possibility%20that%20they%20would%20have%20skipped%20a%20floor%20test.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20also%20said%20the%20BJP%2C%20given%20its%20string%20of%20successes%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Delhi%20assembly%20elections%2C%20did%20not%20want%20a%20crisis%20that%20could%20overshadow%20the%20positive%20political%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20BJP%20chief%20A%20Sharda%20Devi%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20decision%20was%20made%20to%20protect%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20state%20and%20keeping%20in%20mind%20public%20welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%202017%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20been%20working%20tirelessly%20for%20the%20development%20of%20Manipur.%20His%20resignation%20reflects%20his%20deep%20commitment%20to%20safeguarding%20the%20state's%20integrity%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20it%20is%20not%20decided%20yet%20who%20will%20succeed%20Mr%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20posted%20a%20sharp%20comment%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BThe%20resignation%20of%20CM%20Biren%20Singh%20shows%20that%20mounting%20public%20pressure%2C%20the%20SC%20investigation%20and%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20by%20the%20Congress%20have%20forced%20a%20reckoning%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20nearly%20two%20years%2C%20BJP's%20CM%20Biren%20Singh%20instigated%20division%20in%20Manipur.%20PM%20Modi%20allowed%20him%20to%20continue%20despite%20the%20violence%2C%20loss%20of%20life%2C%20and%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20in%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20was%20all%20set%20to%20move%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20his%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20in%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20tomorrow.%20Sensing%20the%20climate%2C%20the%20Manipur%20CM%20has%20just%20resigned%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20post%20on%20X%20from%20Jairam%20Ramesh.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20demand%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20making%20since%20early%20May%202023%2C%20when%20Manipur%20erupted.%20The%20CM's%20resignation%20was%20belated.%20The%20people%20of%20Manipur%20now%20await%20a%20visit%20by%20our%20Frequent%20Flier%20PM%20who%20is%20off%20to%20France%20and%20the%20USA%20now%20-%20and%20who%20has%20found%20neither%20the%20time%20nor%20the%20inclination%20to%20go%20to%20Manipur%20these%20past%20twenty%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clamour%20against%20Biren%20Singh%20grew%20after%20a%20person%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20went%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20alleging%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20instigated%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%20His%20complaint%20was%20based%20on%20leaked%20audio%20tapes%20purportedly%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENon-profit%20private%20forensic%20laboratory%20Truth%20Labs%20confirmed%20that%2093%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20audio%20tapes%20matched%20Mr%20Singh's%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20sought%20a%20report%20from%20the%20Central%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20on%20the%20leaked%20audio%20tapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739121000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fuv6dvaqg_biren-singh-resigns_625x300_09_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.