g%20even%20a%20year%20ago)%20and%20experienced%20the%20joy%20of%20spending%20so%20much%20time%20with%20people%20you%20pick%20up%20on%20each%20other's%20catchphrases%20and%20adopt%20them%20as%20your%20own.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'm%20glad%20there%20are%20books%20on%20how%20to%20make%20friends%2C%20I'm%20grateful%20I%20no%20longer%20need%20to%20consult%20them%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20found%20my%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwas-never-good-making-friends-these-five-things-helped-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739115482000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a4d6b47bb3f854015bfd3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwas-never-good-making-friends-these-five-things-helped-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I've%20learned%20to%20get%20out%20of%20my%20comfort%20zone%20to%20make%20friends.%20I%20also%20learned%20that%20sometimes%20I'm%20the%20one%20that%20needs%20to%20reach%20our%20first.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Brooke%20Metz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwas-never-good-making-friends-these-five-things-helped-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20forces%20withdraw%20from%20key%20Gaza%20corridor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739115180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F02%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-netzarim-corridor-gaza_6823912.jpg%3F20250209141745%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisraeli-forces-withdraw-from-key-netzarim-corridor-in-gaza-13306010%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20forces%20have%20begun%20pulling%20back%20from%20a%20key%20corridor%20through%20Gaza%20as%20part%20of%20its%20ceasefire%20deal%20with%20Hamas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5