2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bisht%20told%20reporters.%20%26quot%3BWhere%20there%20is%20a%20majority%20of%20Hindus%2C%20why%20cant%20it%20be%20Shiv%20Puri%20or%20Shiv%20Vihar%20instead%20of%20Mustafabad%3F%20I%20will%20definitely%20do%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20later%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bisht%20who%20won%20from%20Karawal%20Nagar%20in%20the%202020%20election%20was%20replaced%20by%20Kapil%20Mishra%20this%20time.%20He%20was%20offered%20the%20Mustafabad%20seat%20when%20he%20openly%20expressed%20resentment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2067-year-old%20six-time%20MLA%20had%20beaten%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20Adeel%20Ahmad%20Khan%20in%20Mustafabad%20by%2017%2C578%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20swept%20to%20power%20in%20Delhi%20after%2027%20years%2C%20winning%2048%20of%20the%2070%20assembly%20seats.%20AAP%20won%2022%20seats%20while%20the%20Congress%20failed%20to%20open%20account%20again%20in%20the%20polls%20held%20on%20February%205.%20The%20results%20were%20announced%20on%20Saturday.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739114820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F9l3auf5g_mohan-bisht_625x300_09_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-assembly-election-2025-mohan-bisht-shiv-puri-bjps-mustafabad-mla-proposes-new-name-for-constituency-7672246%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohan%20Bisht%2C%20the%20newly%20elected%20MLA%20of%20Delhi's%20Mustafabad%2C%20the%20area%20that%20bore%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%202020%20riots%2C%20has%20declared%20that%20the%20name%20of%20the%20constituency%20will%20be%20changed%20to%20Shiv%20Puri%20or%20Shiv%20Vihar%2C%20in%20view%20of%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20Hindu%20population%20there%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-assembly-election-2025-mohan-bisht-shiv-puri-bjps-mustafabad-mla-proposes-new-name-for-constituency-7672246%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Zealand%20relaxes%20'golden%20visa'%20rules%20in%20bid%20to%20attract%20wealthy%20investors%20amid%20struggling%20economy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222138%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Auckland%2C%20New%20Zealand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a8a72f7bb3f854015c4b17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221403%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAuckland%2C%20New%20Zealand.%3Cp%3EScott%20E%20Barbour%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20Zealand%20is%20relaxing%20its%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20visa%26quot%3B%20rules%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20lure%20investors%2C%20its%20government%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20visa%20is%20set%20to%20become%20%26quot%3Bsimpler%20and%20more%20flexible%2C%26quot%3B%20Immigration%20Minister%20Erica%20Stanford%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20Zealand's%20economy%20has%20struggled%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20a%20recession%20and%20rising%20unemployment%20in%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-zealand-triples-tourism-entry-fee-to-tackle-environmental-damage-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20Zealand's%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20Sunday%20that%20it%20would%20be%20making%20changes%20to%20its%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20visa%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20lure%20more%20wealthy%20migrants%20to%20its%20shores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErica%20Stanford%2C%20the%20country's%20Immigration%20Minister%2C%20said%20the%20Active%20Investor%20Plus%20(AIP)%20visa%20would%20become%20%26quot%3Bsimpler%20and%20more%20flexible%26quot%3B%20to%20encourage%20investors%20to%20choose%20New%20Zealand%20for%20their%20%26quot%3Bcapital%2C%20skills%2C%20and%20international%20connections%26quot%3B%20and%20as%20a%20place%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuild%20a%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20changes%2C%20which%20are%20set%20to%20take%20effect%20from%20April%201%2C%20two%20new%20investment%20categories%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BGrowth%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBalanced%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20will%20replace%20the%20%26quot%3Bcurrent%20complex%20weighting%20system%20for%20the%20AIP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BGrowth%26quot%3B%20category%20will%20apply%20to%20those%20making%20%26quot%3Bhigher-risk%20investments%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20direct%20investments%20in%20local%20businesses.%20It%20will%20require%20a%20minimum%20investment%20of%20NZ%245%20million%20(around%20%242.8%20million)%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BBalanced%26quot%3B%20category%20will%20focus%20on%20mixed%20investments%20and%20will%20require%20a%20minimum%20investment%20of%20NZ%2410%20million%20(roughly%20%245.7%20million)%20over%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rules%20will%20also%20see%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20English%20language%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIncentivising%2C%20simplifying%20and%20broadening%20the%20investment%20offerings%20will%20make%20New%20Zealand%20more%20attractive%20and%20accessible%20to%20more%20foreign%20high-value%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20Stanford%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20changes%20will%20turbocharge%20our%20economic%20growth%2C%20bringing%20brighter%20days%20ahead%20for%20all%20Kiwis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEconomic%20Growth%20Minister%20Nicola%20Willis%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20be%20rolling%20out%20the%20welcome%20mat%20and%20encouraging%20investor%20migrants%20to%20choose%20New%20Zealand%20as%20a%20destination%20for%20their%20capital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20Zealand's%20economy%20has%20struggled%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20slipping%20into%20a%20technical%20recession%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202024%20and%20seeing%20rising%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHSBC's%20chief%20economist%20for%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Australia%2C%20Paul%20Bloxham%2C%20s