nvestors%20question%20whether%20they%20have%20overvalued%20the%20blue%20chips%20and%20their%20pricing%20power%2C%20especially%20concerning%20their%20proprietary%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20a%20volatile%20ride%20until%20Wall%20Street%20figures%20that%20out.%20For%20now%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-top-ai-stocks-to-buy-bank-of-america-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-related%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20dumping%20almost%20indiscriminately%20or%20at%20the%20slightest%20hint%20of%20a%20slowdown.%20Chip%20designer%20ARM%20was%20a%20recent%20victim%20of%20that%20trend.%20It%20announced%20earnings%20Wednesday%20with%20some%20of%20the%20best%20numbers%20you%20can%20get%20on%20a%20typical%20stock%2C%20said%20Sandeep%20Rao%2C%20a%20quantitative%20analyst%20at%20Leverage%20Shares%20ETPs.%20Still%2C%20the%20stock%20closed%20down%20by%20over%207%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20clearly%20evident%20that%20this%20stock%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20soaring%2C%26quot%3B%20Rao%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20company's%20IP%20is%20used%20in%20virtually%20every%20major%20smartphone%20in%20the%20world.%20Its%20software%20is%20also%20used%20by%20Apple%20computers.%20It%20has%20a%20tie-up%20with%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20its%20backup%20is%20SoftBank%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Stargate%20project%20pumping%20%24500%20billion%20into%20AI%20cloud%20infrastructure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EARM%20CEO%20Rene%20Haas%20also%20welcomed%20DeepSeek%20during%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepseek-hot-topic-earnings-calls-exec-analyst-questions-2025-1%23arm-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFebruary%205%20earnings%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20referring%20to%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bcreative%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20welcomed%20efficiency%20that%20would%20only%20increase%20demand%20for%20computing.%20He%20added%20that%20his%20company%20was%20well-positioned%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20efficiencies%2C%20including%20for%20smaller%20devices%20that%20don't%20require%20high-powered%20Nvidia%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EARM%20isn't%20alone.%20As%20AI%20stocks%20report%20earnings%2C%20they%20find%20themselves%20in%20a%20similar%20predicament%3A%20explaining%20to%20Wall%20Street's%20money%20movers%20that%20they%20are%20well-positioned%20to%20continue%20riding%20out%20the%20AI%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22058c78f8-5f0a-4f8d-afc6-d307e8691088%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20hoarding%20to%20sharing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepseek-switch-ai-startups-struggle-access-chinese-models-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepSeek%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20exactly%20open%20source%3B%20in%20other%20words%2C%20it%20doesn't%20share%20its%20full%20code.%20It's%20open%20weight%2C%20which%20means%20it%20shows%20its%20memory%20or%20knowledge%20process.%20This%20allows%20users%20to%20adjust%20it%20for%20specific%20tasks%2C%20lowering%20the%20bar%20for%20startups%20and%20companies%20to%20enter%20the%20space%20and%20create%20specialized%20business%20models%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20affordability%2C%20increased%20demand%2C%20and%20explosive%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20DeepSeek%2C%20proprietary%20models%20required%20huge%20computing%20power%2C%20which%20meant%20expensive%20and%20small%20supercomputers%20were%20the%20perceived%20solution%20for%20efficiency.%20DeepSeek%20changed%20that%20thesis%2C%20suggesting%20that%20optimization%20isn't%20a%20hardware%20problem%20but%20one%20that%20can%20be%20addressed%20with%20code%2C%20Rao%20said.%20It%20also%20proved%20that%20the%20open-source%20community%20was%20far%20more%20efficient%20at%20driving%20results%2C%20validating%20the%20argument%20that%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20should%20not%20be%20done%20behind%20closed%20doors%2C%20Rao%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20technology%20that%20can%20best%20be%20done%20as%20a%20tide%20that%20lifts%20all%20boats%20instead%20of%20one%20that's%20hoarded%20by%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20terms%20of%20winners%20and%20losers%2C%20investors%20should%20be%20concerned%20with%20the%20picks%20and%20shovels%3A%20companies%20tasked%20with%20building%20AI%20infrastructure%2C%20said%20Abby%20Yoder%2C%20a%20US%20equity%20strategist%20at%20JPMorgan%20Private%20Bank.%20The%20focus%20must%20now%20turn%20to%20their%20revenue%20and%20gross%20margin%20line%20items%20to%20determine%20whether%20they%20will%20see%20the%20impact.%20She%20added%20that%20CapEx%20spending%20isn't%20dropping%3B%20it's%20actually%20increasing%2C%20but%20it%20could%20be%20shifting%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20are%20they%20going%20to%20be%20going%20to%20the%20incumbent%20winners%20that%20we've%20seen%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%20who%20have%20had%20this%20outsized%20pricing%20power%20leading%20to%20those%20really%20high%20margins%3F%26quot%3B%20Yoder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20are%20they%20going%20to%20semiconductor%20companies%20making%20specialized%20chips%2C%20hardware%20providers%2C%20or%20software%20companies%3F%20It's%20the%20key%20query%20investors%20will%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20answer%20if%20they%20want%20to%20continue%20winning%20in%20this%20space.%20On%20JPMorgan's%20part%2C%20the%20investment%20bank's%20North%20America%20equity%20research%20team%20created%20a%20list%20of%20stocks%20they're%20overweight%20on%20and%20that%20they%20expect%20will%20be%20positively%20impacted%20by%20competitive%20and%20efficient%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoftware%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20that%20can%20use%20efficiency%20to%20increase%20their%20total%20addressable%20markets%20will%20be%20the%20new%20big%20winners.%20Here%2C%20Yoder%20believes%20it%20will%20be%20the%20software%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECloud-based%20data%20storage%20provider%20%3Cstrong%3ESnowflake%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(SNOW)%20is%20positioned%20to%20benefit%20from%20increased%20demand%20as%20more%20AI%20applications%20develop%2C%20increasing%20the%20requirement%20for%20data%20storage%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECloud-based%20software%20provider%3Cstrong%3E%20Salesforce%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(CRM)%20could%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20benefiting%20from%20cheaper%20and%20therefore%20increased%20software%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESemiconductors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20semiconductor%20space%2C%20Yoder%20says%20an%20investor%20should%20focus%20on%20those%20gaining%20versus%20those%20losing%20market%20share.%20Overall%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20AI%20chips%20is%20expected%20to%20increase%2C%20not%20drop%2C%20though%20that%20may%20not%20be%20the%20case%20for%20every%20chipmaker%2C%20read%20JPMorgan's%20note.%20Within%20this%20sector%2C%20companies%20that%20provide%20application-specific%20integrated%20circuits%26quot%3B%20(ASICs)%2C%20which%20are%20microchips%20made%20for%20certain%20functions%20instead%20of%20general%20use%2C%20are%20well-positioned%20to%20gain%20from%20the%20increased%20use%20of%20more%20accessible%20AI%20models.%20ASIC%20suppliers%20set%20to%20benefit%20include%20%3Cstrong%3EBroadcom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(AVGO)%20and%20%3Cstrong%3EMarvell%20Technologies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(MRVL).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMicron%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(MU)%20is%20expected%20to%20benefit%20as%20a%20memory%20and%20storage%20chip%20provider%20as%20AI%20adoption%20accelerates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20fears%20about%20how%20necessary%20%3Cstrong%3ENvidia's%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(NVDA)%20expensive%20and%20advanced%20chips%20will%20be%2C%20increased%20demand%20for%20AI%20models%20will%20also%20mean%20increased%20demand%20for%20GPUs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternet%20and%20hyperscalers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big%2C%20leading%20names%20like%20Alphabet%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Meta%20sit%20in%20this%20category.%20Not%20only%20are%20they%20developers%20of%20AI%20models%2C%20but%20they%20are%20also%20the%20spenders%20that%20largely%20determine%20where%20money%20for%20infrastructure%20and%20software%20will%20go.%20Here%2C%20efficiency%20will%20create%20a%20cheaper%20and%20broader%20ecosystem%20for%20AI%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20and%20the%20sharing%20of%20developments%20will%20push%20the%20big%20players%20to%20also%20become%20efficient%2C%20read%20JPMorgan's%20note%2C%20which%20projects%202025%20capex%20spending%20for%20Amazon%20at%20%2497%20billion%2C%20Meta%20at%20%2465%20billion%2C%20and%20Google%20at%20%2462%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20%3Cstrong%3EMeta's%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Llama%20model%20is%20also%20open%20weight%2C%20it's%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20main%20beneficiary%20of%20language%20models%20like%20DeepSeek%2C%20where%20its%20efficiency%20can%20be%20integrated%20into%20Meta's%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%204Q%20earnings%2C%20META%20reiterated%20the%20benefits%20of%20open%20source%20LLMs%2C%20noted%20that%20costs%20can%20be%20driven%20down%2C%20%26amp%3B%20%E2%80%94%20in%20light%20of%20DeepSeek%20%E2%80%94%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20an%20American%20standard%20for%20open%20source%20that%20extends%20globally%2C%26quot%3B%20JP%20Morgan's%20note%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmazon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20also%20not%20shying%20away%20from%20more%20efficacious%20models.%20Its%20cloud-computing%20platform%2C%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%20(AWS)%2C%20has%20already%20added%20DeepSeek%20to%20its%20AI%20platforms%2C%20making%20it%20available%20for%20use%20in%20some%20regions.%20While%20it%20could%20directly%20compete%20with%20more%20expensive%20options%20and%20impact%20pricing%20power%2C%20JPMorgan%20believes%20losses%20could%20be%20balanced%20with%20increased%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlphabet's%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20place%20in%20this%20shift%20isn't%20as%20clear.%20JPMorgan%20believes%20that%20since%20the%20search%20giant%20is%20highly%20dependent%20on%20Gemini%2C%20its%20proprietary%20AI%2C%20there's%20less%20wiggle%20room%20here.%20However%2C%20Google%20can%20use%20lessons%20of%20efficiency%20to%20help%20it%20develop%20its%20own%20path%20to%20building%20out%20its%20models.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20has%20six%20new%20applications%20it%20is%20developing%20and%202%20billion%20users%20it%20can%20distribute%20them%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Marino%2C%20CRO%20of%20Themes%20ETFs%2C%20doesn't%20believe%20that%20large-scale%20institutions%20and%20hyperscalers%20will%20move%20to%20a%20true%20open-source%20model%20solely.%20So%20when%20several%20companies%20maintain%20commitments%20to%20Capex%2C%20it%20means%20they%20haven't%20even%20scratched%20the%20surface%20for%20required%20growth%2C%20this%20includes%20expansion%20into%20agentic%20AI%2C%20which%20are%20models%20that%20can%20make%20decisions%20and%20act%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHardware%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20models%20are%20trained%20and%20built%2C%20the%20key%20part%20is%20their%20use%20in%20the%20inference%20process%2C%20where%20the%20model%20applies%20its%20abilities%20to%20provide%20results.%20As%20demand%20picks%20up%2C%20hardware%20companies%20involved%20in%20this%20process%20are%20set%20to%20benefit.%20These%20include%20%3Cstrong%3EDell%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(DELL)%20%3Cstrong%3ECisco%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(CSCO)%2C%20and%20%3Cstrong%3ENetApp%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(NTAP).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-10-stocks-to-benefit-from-ai-efficiencies-deepseek-jpmorgan-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739107801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a65fbb7bb3f854015c37e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-10-stocks-to-benefit-from-ai-efficiencies-deepseek-jpmorgan-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Investors%20must%20focus%20on%20revenue%20and%20gross%20margin%20line%20items%20to%20determine%20whether%20stocks%20will%20see%20impact.%22%2C%22author%22