n%3EWe're%20taught%20the%20power%20of%20money%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20hanging%20onto%20it%20from%20the%20cradle%2C%20but%20spending%2C%20for%20so%20many%20of%20us%2C%20is%20simply%20a%20reaction.%20A%20thing%20we%20do%20to%20survive%2C%20engage%2C%20and%20indulge.%20No%20one%20teaches%20us%20how%20to%20spend%20for%20the%20same%20reason%20no%20one%20teaches%20us%20to%20breathe.%20They%20assume%20we'll%20figure%20it%20out%20as%20we%20go%20because%20we%20must.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20like%20breathing%2C%20there%20are%20more%20effective%2C%20life-giving%20ways%20to%20do%20it%20than%20others.%20While%20rotely%20participating%20in%20the%20economy%20might%20get%20the%20job%20done%2C%20smart%20spending%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20toward%20giving%20us%20the%20satisfying%2C%20joyful%20lives%20we%20deserve.%20Your%20recognition%20that%20there%20is%20a%20better%20way%20tells%20me%20you%20already%20have%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20find%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20learn%20this%20new%20skill%2C%20however%2C%20you%20may%20have%20to%20unlearn%20many%20of%20the%20ideas%20that%20made%20you%20so%20great%20at%20saving.%20How%20we%20use%20our%20money%20goes%20beyond%20practice%3B%20it's%20our%20worldview%20in%20action.%20You%20said%20it%20best%20in%20your%20letter%3A%20You%20spent%20your%20life%20%26quot%3Bsaving%20for%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%20Covering%20your%20bases%20not%20only%20for%20now%20but%20also%20for%20later%20is%20the%20epitome%20of%20responsibility.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERemember%20the%20fable%20of%20the%20ant%20and%20the%20grasshopper%20%E2%80%94%20the%20grasshopper%20fiddled%20away%20his%20summer%2C%20while%20the%20ant%20spent%20hers%20working%2C%20preparing%20for%20the%20winter%20ahead.%20I'm%20sure%20you%20can%20imagine%20which%20insect%20survived%20to%20see%20the%20spring.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20said%2C%20a%20saver's%20mentality%20is%20future-focused%2C%20while%20someone%20skilled%20at%20spending%20is%20grounded%20in%20the%20present.%20The%20future-focused%20mindset%20is%20often%20motivated%20by%20worry.%20Like%20the%20ant%2C%20that%20worry%20is%20usually%20based%20on%20a%20valid%20forecast%20of%20dormant%20crops%20and%20bad%20weather%20ahead.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20arises%20when%20worry%20becomes%20a%20habit%2C%20and%20the%20rational%20forecast%20morphs%20into%20a%20constant%20state%20of%20doom.%20Saving%20and%20spending%2C%20like%20most%20things%2C%20exist%20best%20in%20balance%20with%20the%20other.%20You%20can%20plan%20for%20the%20future%20while%20enjoying%20the%20present.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20find%20this%20balance%2C%20you%20must%20examine%20your%20relationship%20with%20money%20%E2%80%94%20the%20beliefs%20you%20hold%20about%20it%2C%20what%20you%20believe%20it%20says%20about%20you%2C%20and%20what%20you%20think%20it's%20there%20for.%20You%20wrote%20me%20for%20the%20sole%20purpose%20of%20changing%20your%20mindset%20from%20a%20saver%20to%20a%20spender%2C%20which%20tells%20me%20your%20value%20is%20living%20your%20best%20life%20now%2C%20not%20snoozing%20through%20it%20like%20a%20dragon%20on%20its%20bed%20of%20gold.%20Compare%20your%20beliefs%20about%20money%20to%20this%20value.%20If%20they%20aren't%20compatible%2C%20let%20them%20go.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESometimes%2C%20however%2C%20they%20are%20compatible%20even%20if%20they%20may%20not%20seem%20that%20way%20at%20first%20glance.%20You%20just%20have%20to%20get%20creative.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you%20believe%20that%20%26quot%3Bholding%20onto%20money%20keeps%20me%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20you%20can%20hire%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-online-financial-advisors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efinancial%20planner%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20help%20you%20protect%20your%20retirement%20years.%20If%20being%20