ch.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20incident%20involving%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20occurred.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FPAKvNZ%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23PAKvNZ%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9XTNdqk463%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F9XTNdqk463%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Bemba%20Nation%20(%40BembaNation)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBembaNation%2Fstatus%2F1888443377307287998%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%209%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20from%20NZC%20on%20Ravindra's%20injury%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRavindra%20was%20forced%20from%20the%20field%20after%20being%20struck%20in%20the%20forehead%20by%20the%20ball%20attempting%20a%20catch%20in%20the%2038th%20over.%20He%20sustained%20a%20laceration%20to%20the%20forehead%20which%20has%20been%20addressed%20and%20treated%20at%20the%20ground%2C%20but%20is%20otherwise%20well.%20He%20came%20through%20his%20first%20HIA%20(Head%20Injury%20Assessment)%20well%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20monitored%20under%20HIA%20processes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Zealand%20are%20already%20dealing%20with%20injury%20concerns%20following%20Lockie%20Ferguson's%20hamstring%20injury%20during%20the%20ILT20%20in%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20the%20match%2C%20batting%20all-rounder%20Glenn%20Phillips'%20blitzkrieg%20knock%20powered%20New%20Zealand%20to%20a%2078-run%20victory%20over%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20first%20match%20of%20the%20ODI%20Tri-Series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENZ%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20opted%20to%20bat%20first.%20After%20NZ%20was%20down%20to%2039%2F2%2C%20performances%20from%20Kane%20Williamson%20(58%20in%2089%20balls%2C%20with%20seven%20fours)%2C%20Daryl%20Mitchell%20(81%20in%2084%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)%20and%20Phillips%20(106*%20in%2074%20balls%2C%20with%20six%20fours%20and%20seven%20sixes)%20took%20NZ%20to%20330%2F6%20in%20their%2050%20over