ope%20of%20disability-imposed%20challenges.%20His%20tenacity%20is%20as%20rich%20as%20the%20fragrance%20of%20his%20roses.%20%E2%80%9CDisability%20should%20not%20stifle%20our%20spirit.%20Given%20the%20right%20mix%20of%20positivity%20and%20perseverance%2C%20the%20seeds%20of%20success%20can%20sprout%20in%20the%20most%20unlikely%20of%20places.%20So%2C%20we%20must%20continue%20to%20trust%20ourselves%2C%20remain%20dedicated%2C%20and%20success%20will%20eventually%20follow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99re%20interested%20in%20Rajesh%E2%80%99s%20products%20and%20wish%20to%20support%20his%20venture%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20him%20at%209896167908%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Rajesh%20Kumar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738899551000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Frose-farming-3-1738829624.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D403883%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20vision%20impairment%20and%20financial%20struggles%2C%20Rajesh%20Kumar%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20security%20guard%2C%20transformed%20his%20life%20by%20venturing%20into%20rose%20farming%20%E2%80%94%20eventually%20building%20a%20thriving%20business%20selling%20value-added%20rose%20products.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98No%20One%20Should%20Face%20This%E2%80%99%3A%20After%20Losing%20Daughter%2C%20Dad%20Ensures%20No%20Rare%20Disease%20Patient%20Suffers%20Alone%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20often%20hear%20of%20parents%20building%20their%20savings%20so%20their%20children%20can%20lead%20more%20comfortable%20lives%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20But%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20long%20run%20to%20think%20about.%20I%20just%20had%20the%20present%2